title: Consumer Reports Kitchen Planning & Buying Guide - July 2014
description:
Consumer Reports Kitchen Planning & Buying Guide - July 2014

140 Pages | True PDF | English | 22 MB 


Whether updating your present kitchen or building a brand new one, you will find this guide invaluable.  Beautiful full-color layouts.  How to get the kitchen of your dreams at a price you can afford.  Take the guesswork out of shopping for appliances.  Smart guide to doing it yourself.
